### [Paper](https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.13360) | [Project Page](https://hoar012.github.io/RAP-Project/) | [Model](https://huggingface.co/Hoar012/RAP-LLaVA-13b) | [Data (Coming soon)](https://github.com/Hoar012/Rap-MLLM)

